Marie Csaszar died after a 10-year battle with a brain tumour last September . 
  She worked for seven years at the BBC in Cardiff as a contracts manager . 
  Her husband Paul believes she was 'bullied' by management towards the end of her life . 
  He has asked for her work emails to prove she was being bullied by bosses . 
  BBC has refused to hand over the emails to her widower Paul . 
 